Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:33.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:35.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:39.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学  你还穿的是夏装啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:42.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片你已经换冬装了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:46.37,Takagi san—Picture 04-1,,0,0,0,,{\frz270.6\pos(1668,482)}换装
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:50.75,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因为天气预报说今天会降温
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:54.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,原来西片你还会看天气预报呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.92,0:01:56.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是我大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:02:01.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我在赌我俩会不会在同一天换装  会的话算我赢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:02.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,自作主张比起来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.01,0:02:04.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好吧  就算西片你赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:07.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不不  这感觉胜之不武啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.31,0:02:12.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是  自己挑起比赛又自己认输
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真是蠢到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:17.95,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,而且天气冷了还穿夏装
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:20.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我不怎么怕冷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:23.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,别逞强了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:28.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那么  如果高木同学说冷的话就算我赢如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:33.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我承认冷也能算你赢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:34.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这有什么意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:36.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:41.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,总之  比赛开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:42.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:51.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,虽然有些岔开话题  关于汉字的历史…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:54.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我爸爸又说他看到UFO了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:55.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:57.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,都看清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:58.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:00.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,回去以后一定要给家长看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:13.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我故意今天一整天没有做出让她说冷的举动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:18.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,她一定觉得我已经把比赛的事情给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:21.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,机会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:23.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:25.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,虽然有点唐突  我给你出个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:30.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,本跑得比鲍勃快  但比萨姆慢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:33.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这三个人赛跑的话  谁是最后一名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:34.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是鲍勃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:35.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:37.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那么萨姆是第几名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:41.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,答案是第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:44.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,也就是说  连起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:45.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,萨姆第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:45.99,Takagi san—Picture 04-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1320,648)\clip(1208,282.667,1456,322.667)\t(0,1000,\clip(1208,296,1442.667,698.667))}Sam \N\Nichi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:47.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,萨姆一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:48.12,Takagi san—Picture 04-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1280,672.666)}Samui \N\Nchi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:49.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,冷地！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:54.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果西片说喊疼  就是你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:57.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么说来着  不是按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:03:58.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(941.143,1010)}Seitai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:03:58.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,推拿？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:00.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:02.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(941.715,1010)}itai
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:02.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,背疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:06.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我要把上次被捉弄的份加倍奉还
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:10.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,来吧高木同学  回答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:13.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我想想  萨姆是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:16.15,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:21.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我对了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:22.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:25.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:29.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你想让我说冷字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:34.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,完全束手无策了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:38.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  还有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:41.51,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学以前不是故作从容说过嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:45.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,和天气预报一样  降温了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:47.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:50.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是不是有点冷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:56.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学好像不会对我说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:59.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那她只能同意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果我说「嗯」   你会怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:14.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片会帮我取暖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:21.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,会帮我取暖的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:27.51,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这个…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:30.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:34.35,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,输了  输了  我认输了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:39.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片一遇到这种情况就没辙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:44.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:50.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,既然我赢了  作为惩罚游戏罚你帮我取暖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:51.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:54.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真是的  可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:03.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:08.76,Takagi san—Picture 04-3,,0,0,0,,{\frz271.1\pos(498,414)}冬装
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:15.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,所以说  为什么明明说好了要一起换装  却成这样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:18.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,美奈  你没给早苗发消息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:21.11,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,发过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:22.15,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.82,Takagi san—Picture 04-4,,0,0,0,,{\pos(792,364)}好——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.82,Takagi san—Picture 04-4,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1116,568)}再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.82,Takagi san—Picture 04-4,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034,750)}明天开始穿冬装哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:26.65,Takagi san—Picture 04-4,,0,0,0,,{\pos(740,404)}{\fs90}明天开始穿冬装哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.82,Takagi san—Picture 04-4,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1062,886)}{\fs30}发送失败
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:26.65,Takagi san—Picture 04-4,,0,0,0,,{\pos(882,810)}{\fs55}发送失败
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:26.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这条消息没发出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:32.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:35.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你要怎么补偿我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.79,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,反过来想吧  早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:45.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今天是晴天  很热吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:49.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不换冬装才对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:52.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我都想把袖子卷起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:54.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不如现在就卷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:07:01.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太好了早苗  还好今天很热
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:04.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你脸皮真厚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:06.23,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:16.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:18.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:23.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我也好冷啊  可以把袖子放下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:26.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:36.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好  终于到午饭时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:39.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,带便当了吗  木村
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,他食物中毒请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:45.15,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高尾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:49.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今天是有新游戏发售  逃课了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:52.95,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,樱井  也感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:57.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,偶尔也一个人吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:58.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就是这样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,确实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:12.01,Takagi san—Picture 04-5,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1486,784)}{\fad(400,400)}便当
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:17.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,偶尔一个人吃也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:20.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不仅有窗户  风景不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:21.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,而且最重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:24.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,炸鸡块  是最棒的配菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:41.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,果然还是有点寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:42.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,在这在这
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:46.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,要不要一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:48.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可以是可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:50.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是你为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:54.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因为看西片你孤零零一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:57.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,猜你是不是会寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就来捉弄你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:05.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,觉得我会寂寞就来捉弄我  有点奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:07.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我开动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:24.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片的炸鸡块看起来挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:27.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,要不要用它打赌  和我比赛一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:29.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,出手了啊高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:32.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那么  要是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:34.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就把那个用莲藕做的菜给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:36.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,藕夹是吧  可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:40.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,肉类配菜可是便当的生命线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:43.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我决不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:48.15,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那么  你猜一下这个饭团是什么馅的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:52.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,很单纯但又很难猜  不愧是高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:56.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,能根据高木同学的配菜来推测吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:59.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不行  好像很难
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:00.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,蒙一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:02.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不行  输了炸鸡块就没了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:04.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,风险太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:07.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:14.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,答案是鲑鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:18.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好了  来对答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:24.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学  我可不会看漏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:28.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,旁边的饭团有一点鲑鱼露出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:32.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,藕夹归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:38.03,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,正确答案是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,梅子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:43.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:46.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那我把炸鸡块拿走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:49.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,说的也是  那么精致的便当
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:53.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么能咬定两个饭团是同一种馅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:57.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我的炸鸡块啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:02.51,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看你这么可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:06.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还是用藕夹和你的炸鸡块交换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:08.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:09.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:11.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:15.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那么就换一个惩罚游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:19.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,换一个惩罚游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:29.79,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,惩罚游戏…难道是这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:33.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,要喂我吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:44.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,玩什么好呢  惩罚游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:51.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,难道说  你想让我喂你吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:55.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:56.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:57.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:01.03,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:06.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那可真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:08.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:12.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还是比我一个人吃饭要有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:14.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:18.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那下次还一起吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:19.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:27.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,下次我遂了你的愿  来喂你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:29.35,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,都说了我才不想被你喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:36.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看啊  我昨天拍到了UFO的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:40.40,Takagi san—Picture 04-6,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1532,370)}{\fad(1000,950)}UFO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:43.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好假啊  估计是虫子什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:45.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:48.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,昨晚天空突然闪过一道闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:50.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我一回头  就发现了UFO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:53.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我刚举起镜头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:55.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:58.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,它一瞬间就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}高尾同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你还在相信UFO这种鬼话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:04.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,别用那种怜悯的眼神看我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:05.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,区区日日野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:08.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,区区高尾  那是什么语气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:11.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,对不起对不起对不起对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:12.27,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,而且那张照片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:14.98,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是你单手抛出什么会发光的东西才拍到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:16.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还试了好几次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:19.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你你你你在说啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:21.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我跑步时都看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:31.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那你倒是跟我打声招呼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:34.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我不要  怪恶心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:48.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看起来就是普通的石子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:50.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:53.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我想拍出UFO一样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:56.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,午休的时候高尾他们在闹腾的那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.23,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,UFO真浪漫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:01.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:03.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:08.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我要扔咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:09.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:13.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哎呀  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:16.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这怎么看都只是石子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:18.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是不是扔得不够快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:20.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,总之再来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:21.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:26.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:30.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:32.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,觉得UFO存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,当然存在啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:39.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,干嘛笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:40.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:43.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因为你说得也太理所当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:47.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不说这个  继续扔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:55.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不行吗  要不试试小一点的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:00.67,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学不相信有UFO吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:04.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯…不相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,总觉得很不真实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:09.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你真是不懂浪漫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:11.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,浪漫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:14.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不可以？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:17.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  这样也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:23.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,请继续扔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:29.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,总有点不像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:30.95,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你真执着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:35.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,话说  要浪漫的话还是拍真正的UFO更浪漫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:38.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那要是有真的当然会拍啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:47.67,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果我是外星人  也不会在西片面前现身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我可不想引起骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:55.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不过  出来捉弄一下人好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:01.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果我是外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:04.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就把高木同学这样不相信UFO的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:07.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,全部抓起来然后吓尿他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:11.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我就算被西片抓走也无妨哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:13.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:19.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,刚刚的应该扔歪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:22.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,拍到完美的UFO了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:23.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:25.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:29.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,厉害  跟真的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:32.55,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,把这传到网上一定会引起热议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:34.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我会一炮走红的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:37.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么了  高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:44.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片  那个也许是真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:48.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是啊  拍到巨像真的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:50.11,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不愧是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:56.82,Takagi san—Picture 04-7,,0,0,0,,{\pos(946,254)}豆之汤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:16.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦  不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:19.51,Takagi san—Picture 04-8,,0,0,0,,{\frz269.2\pos(1534,382)}{\fad(360,0)}几小时前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:21.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,诶  今天你要去公共澡堂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:24.35,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯  家里的浴缸坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:25.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:29.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你大概几点去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:32.23,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我想想  大概7点多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:36.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:41.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,…她这么说  我还以为她会等我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:56.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,该说有点失望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:03.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还是说有点寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:09.15,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不不  这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:10.23,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:12.27,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没被捉弄就偷着乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:13.90,Takagi san—Picture 04-9,,0,0,0,,{\frz5.522\pos(800,226)}商品请逐个购买
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:13.90,Takagi san—Picture 04-10,,0,0,0,,{\frz5.382\pos(290,516)}找零·退货
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:16.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,对嘛  喝点水果牛奶静下心来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:21.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,诶  西片是水果派啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:24.95,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我就要咖啡牛奶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:27.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你…你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:28.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:31.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没  还以为你没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:35.51,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,听你这语气  你有在找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,也…没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:41.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我泡澡比较费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:46.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,于是估着西片出浴的时间提前进去泡了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:48.35,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,正如我所料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:52.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,感觉好像输了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:06.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学身上散发着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:08.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,香皂的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:15.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不觉得很新鲜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:18.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我们像这样在夜晚一并走着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:21.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯…也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:24.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,都不太能看清对方的脸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:30.35,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学  要不要来比赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:32.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可以啊  什么比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:35.98,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,先害羞脸红的人就算输
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:37.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:39.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么样高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:42.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因为天色太暗无法确认对方的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:44.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,只有自己坦白才能决出胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:47.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好歹能拉扯到平局
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:51.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可以  不过不可以自己说出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:51.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:55.67,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因为自己又不能知道自己脸红了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:57.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:19:59.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:05.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,虽然很暗  但这个距离就能确认了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:09.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦  你已经脸红了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:11.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是我赢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:14.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,都还没开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:17.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:19.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,被人靠这么近怎么可能不会脸红呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:20.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:23.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那  开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:25.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:27.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,也有可能是泡到脸红了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:30.95,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我倒觉得已经过了很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:33.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我可以再确认一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:35.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:45.43,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真开心呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:48.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,完全被她耍得团团转
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:50.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那我就走这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:52.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:56.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,天色很暗  我送你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:14.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这停顿是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:17.75,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我说什么奇怪的话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:21.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这么黑也看不清她是什么表情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:29.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那句话像是对恋人说的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:34.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是那样吗…我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:36.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我家很近  不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:37.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:46.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我可能也泡得太久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:47.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:49.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:52.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,再见啦  晚上别着凉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:56.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还有西片  你脸很红哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:00.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,都说了是泡到脸红的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:04.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不是  你根本没在看我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.97,0:22:11.10,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}どうして君が泣くの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:16.98,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}まだ僕も泣いていないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:23.28,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}自分より  悲しむから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:30.57,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}つらいのがどっちか  わからなくなるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:38.37,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}ガラクタだったはずの今日が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:45.80,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}ふたりなら  宝物になる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:49.22,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}そばにいたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:58.69,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}君のために出来ることが  僕にあるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:10.28,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}いつも君に  ずっと君に  笑っていてほしくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:22.96,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}ひまわりのような  まっすぐなその優しさを  温もりを全部
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.17,0:23:29.30,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}これからは僕も 届けて行きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:37.43,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}ここにある幸せに 気づいたから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.97,0:22:11.10,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你为何会哭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:16.98,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}明明我还未落泪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:23.28,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}是比我更悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:30.57,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}还是更加痛苦  我已搞不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:38.37,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}本是破铜烂铁的今天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:45.80,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}两人一起的话  就将成为宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:49.22,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}想待在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:58.69,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我能否为你做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:10.28,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}想让你一直笑  想要你永远笑下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:22.96,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}今后我也想想将向日葵般  那直率的温柔和温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.17,0:23:29.30,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}全部送到你心里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:37.43,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}因为察觉到了幸福就在此处
